#: _guides/smallrye-fault-tolerance.adoc
msgid ""
"In this guide, we demonstrate usage of MicroProfile Fault Tolerance annotations such as `@Timeout`, `@Fallback`,\n"
"`@Retry`, `@CircuitBreaker`, and `@RateLimit`."
